@startuml FlinkDistributedJobProcessor
!theme spacelab

actor User
artifact "stream-processor.jar" as JobProcessor

rectangle "Flink Cluster" {
  [JobManager] <<JobManager>>
  [TaskManager 1] <<TaskManager>>
  [TaskManager 2] <<TaskManager>>
  [TaskManager N] <<TaskManager>>
}

User --> JobProcessor : Build Flink Job (JAR)
User --> [JobManager] : Submit JobProcessor
[JobManager] --> JobProcessor : Accepts job
[JobManager] --> [TaskManager 1] : Assign job tasks
[JobManager] --> [TaskManager 2] : Assign job tasks
[JobManager] --> [TaskManager N] : Assign job tasks

JobProcessor ..> [TaskManager 1] : Executes job logic
JobProcessor ..> [TaskManager 2] : Executes job logic
JobProcessor ..> [TaskManager N] : Executes job logic

[TaskManager 1] --> [JobManager] : Report status, checkpoints
[TaskManager 2] --> [JobManager] : Report status, checkpoints
[TaskManager N] --> [JobManager] : Report status, checkpoints

note right of JobProcessor
stream-processor.jar is a Flink job
submitted to the JobManager.
JobManager coordinates execution,
distributes work to TaskManagers.
TaskManagers run the job code in parallel.
end note

@enduml